criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  5-15 years of age at the time of enrollment;

          -  Active in the PDCS

          -  Complete data on age, sex, and ZIKV status;

          -  Willingness to participate in the study visit;

          -  Written parental permission and assent to participate, as appropriate by age.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Children with evidence in their medical charts of a diagnosis of a neurological (e.g.,
             traumatic brain injuries, seizure disorder, stroke) or neurodevelopmental disorder
             (e.g., ADHD, Autism, Intellectual Disability) before January 2016.
